{
  "stem": "15577.5",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And was cooking it in her house, in her place, and was bring, bring-- ah, and my mother was-- with the three or four other women-- was in a special room which was called 'Sick Room.' And she was by herself bringing it and feeding these three or four women and saving them.",
      "word_count": 53
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "What happened when the war ended?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Nobody was left with us, and we were left alone.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it took about two weeks until the Russians came.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They left.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They left after Schindler left.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They ran away.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They ran away.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we were left alone.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then the Russians came and kept us in the camp.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And it took about two or three weeks, and then we were transported, all of us, with the-- again with the cattle train to Poland by the Russians.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Together, it took about three, four days until we were brought to Krakow-- organized.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And most of all ran away immediately.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "After that, came to Germany, and so on.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I went to Germany.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I stayed in Germany.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I started in Germany, and then I went to Israel.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I didn't want to stay with the-- with the Russians, first of all.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't want to stay in Poland.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Poland was, for me, the terrible place.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I stayed there for a few days, maybe a week or two.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I felt very, very not only unhappy.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I felt that I won't find my place in Poland after what happened.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So there was a big trend to-- to leave to the West.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there were possibilities to smuggle through the frontiers, through, again, Czechoslovakia to Germany, because most of the people who were fleeing from the camps were gathered in Germany in the so-called DPs, Displaced Persons camps.",
      "word_count": 36
    }
  ],
